description:
Humans and non-humans!
The "Touhou Seirensen Arrange Pack," a collection of arranged tracks has finally dropped!
Featuring popular songs such as "PLAY MY GAME," "Azure Raindrops," and "Sadistic Love," newcomers Hachimitsu-Lemon and Aftergrow have joined the party!

This pack contains the following: 

■6 Songs
・PLAY MY GAME / A-One
・Azure Raindrops / Akatsuki Records
・The Rise and Fall / DiGiTAL WiNG
・Otogi no Uta / Shinra-Bansho
・FAR AWAY HIGH WAY / Hachimitsu-Lemon × Aftergrow
・Sadistic Love / Silver Forest

 ■6 Challenge Stages
・Lv.5 GAME PLAY (PLAY MY GAME)
・Lv.6 KAPPA PARARA PARARA PARARA♪ (Azure Raindrops)
・Lv.7 Come Fly to Hell (The Rise and Fall)
・Lv.8 Is Hell a Fairy Tale? (Otogi no Uta)
・Lv.9 Let's Destroy It (FAR AWAY HIGH WAY)
・Lv.10 Again Tonight (Sadistic Love)

 * Internet connection required for purchase. 
 * Game must be restarted after songs are purchased in order to use them.
name: Touhou Seirensen Arrange Pack
